descript.abstract: This file is part of the ICAT State Highway Network, which contains the complete road network database submitted by the state DOT, with attribute fields reformatted according to the ICAT highway template, and an attribute field identifying those road segments that are part of the ICAT highway network.
descript.purpose: To provide state highway network datasets for use with the ICAT Highway Network.
descript.supplinf: Attribute Domain Values are included in this metadata. To view Attribute Domain Values via ArcCatalog, choose one of the following Stylesheets from the Metadata toolbar: FGDC FAQ, FGDC Classic, FGDC, or XML.

timeperd.current: Data is current as of date listed.

status.update: The data set may be updated periodically.
